   I always write a Trip Report with text and pictures using MS Publisher
   and will send a copy to Hubert Vereecke when I have finished it. Last
   year, at your request, I produced a résumé in French which is on your
   blog. Briefly, I would say that the trip delivered what was advertised,
   which was a grand tour of NZ. It enabled the participants to get a
   feeling for the country in a short space of time, and from talking to
   friends who have been to NZ, or someone who worked for me who lived
   their for a year, it seemed that we managed to see as much of the
   country as would be feasible in three weeks.

